title: ESPN 30 for 30: Fantastic Lies
description:
ESPN 30 for 30: "Fantastic Lies"

Premiered March 13, 2016 on ESPN.

Summarizes the 2006 event where the Duke Lacrosse team was falsely accused of a gang rape of a black stripper.  The team forfeited their season and three players were wrongly charged before the hoax was fully exposed.

This was a reuploaded from a YouTube rip, and there are a few sections where 10 seconds or so are missing.

Resolution: 764x500 (Set your VLC or other media player to 16:9 to get the proper dimensions.)
Type: MPEG-4, h.264
